Chairman's letter ›
Financial and Corporate Highlights›
Corporate Responsibility Highlights›
Leadership ›





Chairman and CEO Lowell McAdam discusses our 2014 results and Verizon's vision for the future.
We’re focused on delivering growth and profitability – see the results of this balanced approach in financial highlights.
We’re using our technology to solve pressing social issues – creating value for our shareowners, our employees and our communities.
We are guided by a talented and diverse Board of Directors and an experienced senior leadership team.









Investing in Superior Network Technology›
Delivering Innovative Solutions›
Creating a Safer and Smarter World›
Enabling Successful Employees›



Verizon’s network superiority gives us a competitive edge and a platform for offering the growth products of the future.
Verizon is building a pathway to the future through investment in growth businesses and an accelerated innovation process.
Verizon is constantly exploring new ways to use technology to solve pressing social issues in areas such as education and energy management.
Verizon’s important role in the lives of our customers is made possible by our strong, high-performance culture.









View pdf files of our printed annual report, proxy statement and Corporate Responsibility Supplement.

















